#. module: im_livechat_mail_bot
#. nwos-python
#: code:addons/im_livechat_mail_bot/models/mail_bot.py:0
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Good, you can customize canned responses in the live chat application.<br/"
"><br/><b>It's the end of this overview</b>, you can now <b>close this "
"conversation</b> or start the tour again with typing <span "
"class=\"o_nwosbot_command\">start the tour</span>. Enjoy discovering NWOS!"
msgstr ""
"Bagus, Anda dapat menyesuaikan tanggapan otomatis di aplikasi lamaran.<br/"
"><br/><b>Di akhir gambaran umum ini</b>, Anda sekarang dapat <b>menutup "
"percakapan ini</b> atau memulai tur lagi dengan mengetik <span "
"class=\"o_nwosbot_command\">mulai tur</span>. Enjoy discovering NWOS!"

#. module: im_livechat_mail_bot
#: model:ir.model,name:im_livechat_mail_bot.model_mail_bot
msgid "Mail Bot"
msgstr "Bot Email"

#. module: im_livechat_mail_bot
#. nwos-python
#: code:addons/im_livechat_mail_bot/models/mail_bot.py:0
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Not sure what you are doing. Please, type %s and wait for the propositions. "
"Select one of them and press enter."
msgstr ""
"Kami tidak yakin dengan apa yang Anda ingin lakukan. Mohon ketik %s dan "
"tunggu saran. Lalu pilih salah satu dan pencet enter."

